Ah, aku siapa?

355
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:32,150
Yang kutemui di rumah sakit itu?

356
00:19:32,150 --> 00:19:35,790
Choi Eun Yoo kau beli dengan apa?

357
00:19:36,120 --> 00:19:38,820
Kubeli masa depan wanita itu.

358
00:19:39,260 --> 00:19:41,060
Sebetulnya hanya beberapa ribu won saja.

359
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:42,660
